                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Et ne me donne aussi sa foi",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Pour me la reprendre de même.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je n’aimerai jamais que toi…\nA moins qu’une femme ne m’aime,\nEt ne me donne aussi sa foi\nPour me la reprendre de même."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Car, vois-tu, nous ne pouvons pas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Si forte qu’en soit notre envie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Aux liens frêles de vos bras",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Dérober jamais notre vie.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Car, vois-tu, nous ne pouvons pas,\nSi forte qu’en soit notre envie,\nAux liens frêles de vos bras\nDérober jamais notre vie."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Nous prenons nos amours brisés",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Pour nous en forger d’autres chaînes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "— O contagion des baisers,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Défaillances toujours prochaines !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Nous prenons nos amours brisés\nPour nous en forger d’autres chaînes.\n— O contagion des baisers,\nDéfaillances toujours prochaines !"
        }
